values:
mmm sick again
i've been to the doctor 3 times this month
all they do is play finding nemo in the waiting room
i hate nemo... i must kill nemo
but anyway....
well monday was a snow day!! and andrew wuz ungrounded!!
we had band practice with all 3 of us for the first time in a month then me andrew and chris met up with jen jay kaleigh crystal and mike and we all went to jays to watch our home movies we made in the summer... there so funny.. MATEING SEASON MATEING SEASON...im not saying anything or that certain person will get mad LMAO
on weds. me jay max bryan and brenden went to woodland while they were still having 9th period... jay and bryan decided to start wrestling in front of the whole skool... 300-400 kids must have been cheering them on.. funny as hell
we said hi to our old bus driver, marvin
he was actually pretty nice to us... considering the fact that toward the end of the year he found out we were sneaking on his bus.. he was always talking about me and jay (mostly jay) disrespecting him... i wonder what he could be talking about?

heyyyyy yesterday was the trinity showww
so much fun hanging out with jen<3 chris kaleigh joe max and matt and others
went to taco bell and me and max had a quick crab fight lol
as for the show... we played pretty good but it just wasnt the same with andrew not there 
but theres awesome news that andrew is playing the image bar with us... that should be a kickass show.. from 1:30 to 8:00 on saterday.. feb. 05 
we are going on at 4:50 - 5:15 
if u want to go please either go to me or chris and i guess andrew b/c we have tickets to the show.. there $10 each 
until then
peace out my home slices
-matt

hey i havent updated this thinger in a while...
alot of my friends are grounded
today me and jays older brother mike thought it would be funny to run in while jason is in the shower and pour apple juice on him so he would think it was piss.... lets just say he got mad... lol it was funny though... hes grounded
andrew is ungrounded i think at the end of this month so thats good
last night at calvary was awesome.. got to hang out with jen and were going out : )!! so last night was awesome
WOOO this friday is the trinity and i think were playing last!!
its all the way in glen cove though 
on feb 5th weve got the show at the image bar so if you want to go please tell me.. i have 10 tickets and so does chris

ahhhhhh life is going just great...
andrew gets burned on his face b/c hes stupid and now i hear he has to get plastic surgery 
and now hes grounded 4 god knows how long and i dont know if he is gonna miss the show at trinity... if he would just shut the fuck up and listen to what his parents have to say then they might let him play... but doesnt seem to be going too well....
why does something bad happen everytime we have a show coming up soon

im really really boreddddddddddddddd
the vacation is more than half way over n i still havent started that damn asl project... i hate asl 
but anyway... i just saw meet the fockers..... funny movie, ass-hoooooooole lol that wuz greaaat, saw it with andrew, crystal, kaleigh, chris, john, tommy-lee. 
i went to a surprise party for chris t. the other day.. it was fun, while i took part in hugging the giant snowman infront of some guys house.... he was a friendly snowman
well the night before i wuz over jays house for the night b/c my sister wuz having a huge sleepover at my house.... so glad i wuznt there.. well while i wuz at jays i realized i was the TAMPON MASTERRRRRR... yes thats right .... the TAMPON MASTERRRRRRR.  went into the womans bathroom and took about 20 tampons... then in the morning i threw them all over his room, his brother mike got pissed, n made us look for them n pick them up, i decided to go back to sleep, haha jay hadda get them himself.... stupidass lol
well im prob off to sleep...

yay its xmas.... and i just got a brand new marshall half stack.... im so happy b/c its so awesome, cant wait to start using it during practice
well dec. 23 was the homeless run then the lock in at calvary.... awesome time... everyone keeps on making fun of me b/c i went to sleep with a teddy bear that nat gave to me for the night.... i named it mr. snuggles lol
I got back from that at like 7 am... i was really tired to i went back to sleep, and all i remember is feeling something hit me in the face, opening my eyes and seeing jay go, "merry xmas u bastard"
Also i watched NAPOLEAN DYNAMITE for the first time... lmao that was the funniest movie ever... "hey napolean can i get some of your tots" and "dont worry napolean, one day youll find a babe, peace out" lol that was great

well we put 2 new songs on the purevolume site, so please check it out : )
kk l8er

heyyyyyyy its sunday...
just got back from the city with the calvary, fun stuff.  Alot of fun moments, lmao chris's mom told me that for breakfast.... chris ate this dinasour cereal where there just eggs, but when you add milk, the eggs hatch into dinasours.  wtf is that lol.  The best part was deff. when dave took the free stress test on the street and when he was done this lady would not let him walk away without buying a book.  
Lady : would you like to buy a book?
dave : im not much of a reader
lady : thats ok we have a dvd
dave : dammit

well for the band, we've got another show which is at the Trinity Church in glen cove on jan 21st (i think)woooootttt!!!!!
its only a couple more days until christmas, and a couple more days until i get my new amp

yea im bored .. its like 12 at night and i decieded to make one of these..got home awhile from jays watching gremlins 2... awesome movie.
today was weird, found out andrew now cant make it to our feb. 5 show at the image bar... i got annoyed... then i went to taco bell and ate some tacos.. i felt better after that!!! but everything is cool b/c we found someone to take his spot that night, nat said hed do it which it awesome n he is saving our asses.. woot woot..
yesterday was another normal day at school.... exept for the fact that kate gave me this really cool hella awesome purple scarf/shirt?.... i wore it to some classes for good luck... my teachers freaked out... its  all good...last night was the show at calvary ... had fun.. good bands...
